title: Post-hoc tests for classic 1-way ANOVA — postHocTest

Default Tukey's test. Tukey HSD's test compares possible pairs means, based studentized range distribution. used TukeyHSD() function, can applied balanced designs (number samples group), also midly unbalanced designs. Dunnett's test compares single control group groups. Make sure factor levels properly ordered.
